

<h3>Taxi delicensing scheme</h3>

<p>TfL has re-launched its enhanced delicensing fund that supports taxi drivers who want to delicense their Euro 3, 4 or 5 vehicles.</p>

<p>Following the announcement of &pound;24m funding from the Mayor, TfL has restructured the taxi delicensing scheme.</p>

<p>Payments of up &pound;8,000 are now available to current applicants having allocated all the payments at the &pound;10,000 and &pound;9,000 level. We continue to accept applications which will be allocated to the appropriate level on a first come, first served basis.</p>

<p>Applicants that have already been allocated and paid at the &pound;9,000 and &pound;8,000 level may have their payment upgraded following a full reconciliation of applications. If you receive an email from TfL offering a top up payment of &pound;1,000, please provide the requested information so we can make the additional payment. If you have any queries about the this top up payment, please email <a href="mailto:taxidelicensing&#64;tfl.gov.uk">taxidelicensing&#64;tfl.gov.uk</a> or call 020 3054 5437</p>

