<h3>Taxi Age Limits</h3>

<p>Following a <a href="https://consultations.tfl.gov.uk/tph/taxi-age-limits/">public consultation</a>, we will be introducing changes to taxi vehicle age limits and exemptions. These changes are being introduced in order to reduce harmful emissions from taxis and improve air quality in the capital.</p>

<p>The <a href="https://consultations.tfl.gov.uk/tph/taxi-age-limits/user_uploads/taxi-age-limits-consultation-report.pdf">taxi age limits consultation report</a> and <a href="https://consultations.tfl.gov.uk/tph/taxi-age-limits/user_uploads/taxi-age-limit-decision-paper.pdf">decision paper</a> which summarises the consultation report and makes recommendations to the Commissioner, is available for download.</p>

<p>Please visit our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/info-for/taxis-and-private-hire/emissions-standards-for-taxis">Emission Standards for Taxis</a> page for more information about how this may affect you.</p>
        

       




 